  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive placeable decal, to add flair and decoration to bases.<br><br>This decal commemorates the collective effort of the Travellers in mapping the <span class=\"name name-special\">Histiographical Flux</span> and tracking the renegade echo during the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Beachhead</span> Expedition.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的可放置贴花，为你的基地增添风格和美观。<br><br>此贴花纪念了在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">抢滩</span>远征期间，旅行者为绘制<span class=\"name name-special\">史学波动</span>地图和追踪反叛者的回音所付出的共同努力。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的可放置貼花，可以裝飾基地，增添個人風格。<br><br>這片貼花紀念了旅行者在定位<span class=\"name name-special\">史學史通量</span>，及於<span class=\"name name-stellar\">灘頭</span>探險中追蹤叛離者回音的集體貢獻。"
  },
